One more issue

Even after fixing the SR-IOV mismatch, your node still has:

16 GiB / 18 GiB hugepages already allocated.

Your pending pod requests 8 GiB hugepages.


So you'll also need to free hugepages or increase the node's hugepage allocation before that pod can be scheduled.

